urls.description: Vestas is a leading offshore wind turbine manufacturer with 8 + GW of offshore wind installed to date. We are the preferred supplier for the 2.1 GW Empire Wind offshore project in New York as well as Atlantic Shores’ 1.5 GW offshore project in New Jersey. The two projects will generate enough clean energy to power over a million U.S. homes each year. 1,2 Offshore wind presents real opportunities to create good-paying jobs and long-term investments here in the U.S. Vestas is taking an active role in
